race.comment: ZULU MAY (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (20.56) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Should bounce back. FEATHERS MY MATE (6) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Talk About Turbo (20.59) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. ONE NUMBER AWAY (8) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 340m behind Liar Guy (20.84) in a Grade 5. Should be about the money. QUITE PROMISING (2) can feature with the right run.
